title: Anna's Birthday w/ Jason Mantzoukas, Paul Scheer and June Diane Raphael

description:
In this week's episode, Anna and Sim sit down with the insanely funny hosts of the popular movie podcast HOW DID THIS GET MADE?, June Diane Raphael (Grace and Frankie, Ass Backwards), and Unqualified repeat guests Paul Scheer (The League, Fresh Off The Boat) and Jason Mantzoukas (The League, The Dictator)! June and Paul go on a double-date with Jason and his new girlfriend, Kayla, and take a meeting with the most powerful woman in Hollywood, Karen Sarducci! June and Paul also share the story of how they fell in love, and the gang calls Gabby who’s deciding whether to meet up with someone she’s met online.

Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
